{"actor":"Chadisfaction","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-12T03:01:25Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":105,"issue_id":"pixelated-vgk","new_value":"{\"notes\":\"Work started.\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"pixelated-vgk\",\"title\":\"Execute Stage 1 Foundation Training\",\"description\":\"📀 OVH Golden Image Strategy - Infrastructure Ready, Backend Blocked\\n\\n## ✅ Progress Update (2026-03-10)\\n\\n### Completed:\\n1. **Docker Image Built Successfully**\\n   - Fixed Dockerfile base image: `nvidia/cuda:12.1.0-devel-ubuntu22.04`\\n   - Removed 8GB+ dataset COPY (causing build timeouts)\\n   - Added S3 download at runtime (boto3) for datasets\\n   - Image: `pixelatedempathy/training-node:stage1` (24.6GB)\\n   - Pushed to Docker Hub\\n\\n2. **Training Script Updated**\\n   - Added `download_datasets_from_s3()` function to train_ovh.py\\n   - Datasets download from OVH S3 at container startup\\n   - Prevents DATASYNC_RETRY_ERROR by avoiding baked-in datasets\\n\\n3. **Existing LoRA Checkpoint Found**\\n   - Location: `archive/failed_attempts_2026-02-24/therapeutic_ai_final_stage1/`\\n   - Size: ~39MB adapter (base: LatitudeGames/Wayfarer-12B)\\n   - Config: r=16, lora_alpha=32\\n\\n### ⚠️ Blocker: OVH Backend Bug\\n\\n**Error:** `403: forbidden, pci project status is \\\"\\\"`\\n\\n**Root Cause:** OVH AI Training API backend bug - \\\"pci project status\\\" lookup returns empty for our project. This is a **known OVH infrastructure issue** documented in:\\n- `/docs/operations/ovh-ai-training-troubleshooting.md` (Section 0)\\n- `/agent/internal/OPERATIONS.md`\\n\\n**Evidence:**\\n- JWT token valid (expires April 2026)\\n- Project ID `49c5c322-6340-459a-8dea-2fcfd6237e7f` correct\\n- Region US-EAST-VA properly configured\\n\\n**Resolution Required:** OVH Support escalation\\n\\n### 📋 Next Steps:\\n1. **Escalate to OVH Support** with:\\n   - Error: `403: forbidden, pci project status is \\\"\\\"`\\n   - Project ID: `49c5c322-6340-459a-8dea-2fcfd6237e7f`\\n   - Console shows \\\"account already authorized\\\"\\n\\n2. **Alternative:** Wait for OVH backend recovery\\n\\n3. **Alternative:** Try new application token via OVH AI Dashboard\\n\\n### 🚀 Ready to Launch (When OVH Recovers)\\n```bash\\nsource .env \\u0026\\u0026 ovhai job run \\\\\\n  --name \\\"stage1-foundation-training\\\" \\\\\\n  --flavor l40s-1-gpu \\\\\\n  --timeout 24h \\\\\\n  --env OVH_S3_BUCKET=\\\"${OVH_S3_BUCKET}\\\" \\\\\\n  --env OVH_S3_ENDPOINT=\\\"${OVH_S3_ENDPOINT}\\\" \\\\\\n  --env OVH_S3_ACCESS_KEY=\\\"${OVH_S3_ACCESS_KEY}\\\" \\\\\\n  --env OVH_S3_SECRET_KEY=\\\"${OVH_S3_SECRET_KEY}\\\" \\\\\\n  -v training-checkpoints@GRA:/checkpoints:rw \\\\\\n  pixelatedempathy/training-node:stage1 \\\\\\n  -- python /app/ai/training/ready_packages/platforms/ovh/train_ovh.py --stage stage1\\n```\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"chad@pixelatedempathy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-11T23:40:24Z\",\"created_by\":\"Chadisfaction\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-11T23:40:24Z\",\"due_at\":\"2026-03-09T00:00:00Z\"}"}
